# rule.forbid.timestamps-in-route-artifacts

route artifacts must not include timestamps. dates (YYYY-MM-DD) ok; time precision not.

## .why

timestamps = false precision, merge conflicts, complex diffs.

## .pattern

```jsonl
// good
{"stone": "1.vision", "status": "passed"}
{"stone": "1.vision", "status": "passed", "on": "2026-03-08"}

// bad
{"stone": "1.vision", "status": "passed", "at": "2026-03-08T12:34:56Z"}
```

## .enforcement

timestamp fields in route artifacts = **BLOCKER**
